// ** React Imports
import { useContext } from 'react'

// ** Reactstrap Imports
import { Row, Col, Card, CardBody, CardTitle, CardText } from 'reactstrap'

const AccessControl = () => {
  return (
    <Row>
      <Col md='6' sm='12'>
        <Card>
          <CardBody>
            <CardTitle tag='h4'>Common</CardTitle>
            <CardText>Card 1</CardText>
            <CardText className='text-primary'>Users</CardText>
          </CardBody>
        </Card>
      </Col>
    
        <Col md='6' sm='12'>
          <Card>
            <CardBody>
              <CardTitle tag='h4'>Analytics</CardTitle>
              <CardText>Card 2</CardText>
              <CardText className='text-danger'>Admins</CardText>
            </CardBody>
          </Card>
        </Col>

    </Row>
  )
}

export default AccessControl
